IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User mcardiff@hawk.iit.edu
PassCmd "printf %s $(grep hawk ~/.config/.authinfo | grep -Pzo 'password.(.*)' | sed -e 's/password //')"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/Gmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/Gmail/Inbox

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Trash"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount brandeis
Host imap.gmail.com
User mcardiff@brandeis.edu
PassCmd "printf %s $(grep brandeis ~/.config/.authinfo | grep -Pzo 'password.(.*\\n)' | sed -e 's/password //' | tr -d '\\n')"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore brandeis-remote
Account brandeis

MaildirStore brandeis-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/Brandeis/
Inbox ~/Mail/Brandeis/Inbox

Channel brandeis
Far :brandeis-remote:
Near :brandeis-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Trash"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
